messages.content: "Why wouldn't I be?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: He gives her a side-eye. "Car accidents are one of the most common causes of death the world over, Magnolia. Or do you just throw your life to the wind without checking?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "Nobody was meant to be sent hurtling through the air at inhuman speeds, trapped in a tiny metal box filled with lighter fluid and explosions." This is a very original observation.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: He sighs and puts a hand on her shoulder. "But it's alright. I can extend some forgiveness."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "I was hesitant to take my chances with the police. I do avoid vehicles other people are driving in most cases, though. It's not exactly an ideal method of transport."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "I'm very glad to hear that."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: Where is this hallway going?

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: It could lead any number of places, depending on the route taken. Viotto's been here before; depending on what he's attempting to find, he could probably make his way to its location on the ship.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Well, really, he's looking for the helm...

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: Viotto and Magnolia arrive at the closest thing to a helm this ship has, the area on the highest floor. Magnolia finally sees the position of this vessel in space, that being high up, and does a double take.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "See? An airship, as I said. You should hardly be surprised."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: He looks around for the annoying ship-related woman.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content:
Right on time, she arises to the area from a different set of stairs, narrowing her eyes at you.

"Is this who you were talking about?" Magnolia.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Yes, of course. Say hello to Fema."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: He waves.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: Magnolia waves after a slight delay.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "How's it been going around here, then? Any new conflict for us to have, or can we skip to the part where we struggle to figure out how to leave?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: Viotto is feeling very cynical today.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: Hopefully he's expressing that well.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: ((He is.))

author.name: zzazz
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\00e5cb55aacbe3824e8b8a9d53aac811-1CCD0.png

messages.content: "I'm out of things to say to you." Nerissa. "Are you truly incapable of leaving?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "I'm very capable of it. I'm just unable to figure out the method."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "Would you be so kind as to escort me and my daughter to a functioning elevator?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "Daughter." Nerissa grimaces. "I do not know what an elevator is. But I've already shown you the way out, haven't I?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "...no. We haven't moved at all since this conversation started. Are you okay?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "I have not shown you right this second, no. Do you truly lack a longer memory?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "I fear she's gone senile, Magnolia. Let's head back and search for a way out ourselves."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: He walks back to where they came from.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content:
Magnolia looks in confusion at Nerissa, but does ultimately follow.

They return to that same room.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Viotto heads into the smaller room on the far left. If it doesn't take him anywhere, he tries each one sequentially.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: Viotto eventually gets into one that works, tripping over before finding himself in a dark room with a single exit.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Assuming that exit is different from the door that he just came through, he heads towards it.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: Wait.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: He turns around and checks to see if Magnolia followed.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: She's not here.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Ugh. We're wasting time here! We're falling behind!

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: He steps cautiously back through the door to nag her.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content:
Miraculously, he makes his way back to the other room.

"Was there something in that one?" Magnolia is leaning against a wall.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Well, I wouldn't know! Because you didn't come check it with me! What are you doing in here? Do you want to stay in one place forever?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "There was an exit in there. Just... follow me."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: He heads back through the door, this time set on making it all the way to the exit.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content:
"Okay, I guess."

Magnolia and him end up in that same smaller room. "What?" She sighs. "This day is awful. Am I not awake right now?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "No, you're absolutely awake. We both are. That's the one thing I'm certain of here."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: He walks.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content:
Outside the one exit, the next room appears to be floating in a void, but it seems like there are still translucent walls bounding it. 

To the left is another door, and to the right the room continues, becoming brighter and brighter to the point where it can no longer be discerned.

Opposite the door Viotto just went through, what appears a giant turtle is floating within the void. 

A young boy probably in his teens walks over from the right, stares at you, and then runs through the door to the left.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: What the fuck?

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: ...is there nothing at all I can see through the semi-transparent walls?

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content:
It looks kind of like a generic space background.

After a brief moment, Rikarasu "Fainda Shinjitsu" Endo comes out of the door to the left.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: ((like, stars?))

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: ((Sure, yeah.))

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Ichigo is pushing boxes.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Making steady progress, indeed...

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "Uchigo, what are your thoughts on that woman, exactly? I just can't discern your relationship."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: Might as well strike up some conversation while we have the chance.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: Ichigo listens silently and then takes some time to formulate a response. “We only met for work at first. But I got to know her through time passed. I couldn’t admit it, but I enjoyed to act as her assistant.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: “She is smarter than she seems. But she is also dumber than she seems. It’s weird.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Ah, well, I find that applies to everyone. Human appearance is a game of compromises." He chuckles.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "So, you're her assistant, huh? And yet you seem to do most of the work around here. Curious, isn't it?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "What's your career trajectory looking like?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: “My mother is well off but unstable in finance. I’m studying for school, specifically for medicine. She has a lot of faith in me.” He looks up. “I hope she can excuse me being gone for… this.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "It's fantastic that you're so independent. I'm positive she couldn't resent you for that fact."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "But why would a student of medicine be working with a petty detective? One of those fields is clearly a preferable use of time, if you don't mind me saying."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: “I…” His expression darkens. “Mother originally sent me to see how R…Fainda performed. She’s the one who hired Fainda for her own reason. I don’t think I can trust you with that reason. Sorry.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "...hm. I respect the predicament you're in. I hope that someday... we can reach that level of trust, even if you don't feel the same way."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: He scratches he neck and gets back to the boxes.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: His mother? Really? That incompetent detective is here with... the son of her employer?

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: What kind of conflict of interest is that, even?

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: And did he really call his own mother unstable?

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: What a family...

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: The boxes are in position. This causes the keyhole on the door to rotate upside down. Nothing else happens.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Viotto hadn't really noticed the keyhole before now. He goes to look through it.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: It’s dark, but you can vaguely see what looks like a room through it.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: He takes another electrical hazard sticker out of his coat and attempts to stick it through the abnormally large hole.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: It fails to find a surface to stick onto and just falls to a point within the hole.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Well, I suppose this door does actually lead somewhere.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "Any ideas, boy?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: “Perhaps there is more to the initial room than thought. My search there was briefer than we’ve undertaken here. I don’t know what this progress means.” He looks at the keyhole.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Hm. Why don't we go check, then?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: He nods.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Viotto sets his course to the staircase they came in from. Although he had certainly hoped the reprieve from the others would be longer.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

“Oh. Hm.” 

Voreverl briefly gives an inscrutable glance at the Pope.

“Yes, that would check out with my understanding. It was indeed the police. You are still wanted for murder, technically.”

author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: But how could Viotto possibly address this?

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: There is no indirect method here... there's no missing information. He just has to bite the bullet.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "I've met this 'Bernard' before, however. Whether that is an alias or whether they were using one when we met, I could not say, but they attempted to murder me. Repeatedly. I feel incredibly unsafe in here, you know." He smiled.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "Perhaps you could... explain how she has been reformed...?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "Or, if you were kept in the dark on this information..."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "They even seem to be concealing their sex. I could not say what else they have hidden from either of us."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content:
“Oh, come on! It’s not that hard, fogey.” Bernard yells.

“Don’t be rude!” He is chastised by the pope.

Nevertheless, he continues. “Did you not yourself meet someone who was behaving the *exact same* as Voreverl Leocot in Arctica, claiming to be her, despite having a completely different body? What did you think of that, huh?”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Yes. You have, indeed, haunted me across several locations while constantly changing your appearance. Is that meant to... convince me of something?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "I see past these hollow indicators, into the heart of a person. That is my very purpose on this earth."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: He smiles at his Holiness.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content:
“No.” His Holiness rebuffs this. “This body was Bernard’s to begin with, anyway. Much in the sense that your body on Earth is occupied by nobody when you are in Arctica, ‘Voreverl’s body’, or, this one…”

“God! Who cares?!” Bernard stops the car. “We’ve driven far enough.” He turns to Viotto. “Here’s the deal. You *know* Voreverl. You’ve *talked* to Voreverl. Do you think she’s capable of any meaningful act of deception? That she could lie to someone about her identity without an immediate compulsion to scream about how she’s lying and that she’s Voreverl Leocot? *Really?* You seem like you think highly of pope, so do you seriously think he can be duped by the living equivalent of a strawman argument?! Get real.” He tosses a small object onto Viotto’s lap.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Voreverl is the greatest deceiver I've ever known."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: He glances down at the object.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "Even Adam, God's original servant in his image, was fooled by the snake with ease..."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "For reasons I barely need to mention."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content:
The object is a PDA. Like the one Viotto has. But it doesn’t light up at all. It’s dead. “The guy who can make that usable by being present isn’t *here*.”
Bernard gets out of the car. “Look, whatever. I’m gonna… sit in this field for a bit. You talk to him.”

“Ah, okay.” The pope waves. ((end sesh))

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: ((session next week))

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Look, I understand your... trepidation. Truthfully, whoever we call that boy, he's not quite alright. But I've been aware of this all along."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: ((momento))

author.name: bloopiero
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\d99c460ae22eacecb7185aae4c31f492-452CA.png

messages.content: ((the pope is saying this right))

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: ((yes))

author.name: zzazz
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\00e5cb55aacbe3824e8b8a9d53aac811-1CCD0.png

messages.content: ((yes))

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "ᵀʰᵃᵗ ᵍᶦʳˡ, ʸᵒᵘ ᵐᵉᵃⁿ..."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "Why have you kept him around so long, in that case...? Is it... do you intend to heal him, spiritually?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "Or are there... other temptations at play here?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: He side-eyes the pope.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "As an 'in' to The Antarctica Project. Voreverl lived right around here at the time of its beginning, so her presence would be the easiest to manage, regardless of disposition."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "What is The Antarctica Project?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "An elaborate scheme that aims to supplant reality. I, of course, have stake in the world created for us by God than that man crafted in his hubris."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "What man..."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: He leans in close.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "I mean the proper noun. Like 'That which Man created.' Though if you want a spearheading figure to blame, the closest is probably Culbasko. Intelligence on the front of everyone responsible is a bit vague because of certain uncooperative entities."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Can you tell me more about a man named Sheeval Deltent?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: I need to know...

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "Hm. I don't know anything offhand. The name feels a little familiar... I've probably read it before, but I can't recall where. I apologize I can't be of more help."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "What do you mean... you can't recall? No... it's not enough to apologize. You need to remember this."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "Come on. Tell me."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: I smile.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "I'm really unable to say offhand." The Pope takes out an iPhone. "Hrm. Looks like he's a--oh, that's where I heard it! The man you killed, allegedly."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Francis... you said you were gathering intelligence on people involved, however vague that may be. And Sheeval is a self-admitted leader of this project. How can you... claim ignorance? Right to my face?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "He claimed that? It seems evident he is doing no leading now, at least. It seems he does have the set of connections that would make that kind of role feasible, but he was never someone solidly connected to anything. Not by anyone willing to share that information with me. There is a large amount of indirection involved in all of this."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Who is unwilling to share relevant information with *you*? Why are you not... directness itself, as you have been pre-ordained to be?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "Indirection is only useful in context, not as setup. You must understand what kind of situation you're in..."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "Sir."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "I cannot afford to focus all of my attention on this matter. There is a church and a nation to run, an entire population to determine how I communicate with. That the manner of delegation on this front could be more productive has become obvious, however."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Can I be frank, Frank? What am I doing here? What use could you possibly have for one as lowly as I, except, perhaps, to... delegate to me? Is that my position here?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content:
"Perhaps. It depends on if you are willing to cooperate."

Bernard is done sulking, and re-enters the car. "Are we done? Where does this guy go from here?"

The Pope is silent.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "I offer my heart and soul to you fully, your Excellency. Please. I could not be more cooperative."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content:
“That is good to know.”
Bern laughs. “Is that was this is about? Need a guy in TAP that’s less schizo so you can throw me out?”
The pope shakes his head at this rambunctious child.
“I have no desire to be that rude to you, but there’s no harm in doing everything we can. You say you don’t trust Voreverl either, right?”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Viotto wonders what it means to be 'in tap'.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "Of course not."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content:
“No, I don’t.” Bernard responds. It will remain ambiguous who the Pope was actually asking. “But it’s about weighing risks. You *get* Voreverl, yeah? You’ve gotten this far. I feel the same way. She’s pretty consistent when you get down to it. But I got no idea who the hell this man is. Stinks to high heaven. It’s the devil you know vs the devil you don’t, right?”

“I would prefer no devils at all.” The Pope.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "The devils will not be gone from this world in your lifetime. If what you fear is the one you don't know, it seems that the sensible solution is to gain that knowledge, eh?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: He reaches out for a handshake.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content:
The Pope lacks confidence that the handshake is for him, and thus does not reciprocate. Bern does not interpret it as being for him either. It’s awkward.
“A very good point. Even in the worst case scenario, it is better to find out if Viotto could be problematic to our goals now rather than when it’s too late. Disregarding that I highly doubt he is.”
Bern pouts. “Why, cuz he sucks up to you?”
The Pope sighs. “I don’t expect you to understand the cultural context, but this is more meaningful than base tribalism. I never wanted to discount your aid on account of faith; lest we forget the Good Samaritan. But fundamentally, Viotto shares the same sort of values I do. When it comes down to it, your priorities will likely diverge from mine. …Please drive us the rest of the way to the Vatican.”

Bern slams on the gas spitefully, acquiescing. “Ridiculous. Like he could even…”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: The handshake was clearly for Bernie.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: Unfortunately, taking his hand off the wheel to try again seems like a poor move...

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "You know... Bernard... the catechumenate is available to anyone. Even you."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "You sit next to the most morally righteous man you may ever meet. Do you truly feel nothing?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content:
"I don't know what that is and it sounds like a drug."

"He means conversion, Bernard."

"Why does everyone assume I'm gay?!"

"No, as in..." The Pope is caught off guard by this outburst and stops talking.

"Look, this guy isn't even the most morally righteous person I know to be named Jorge. I've got nothing against him, but really? Even you don't believe he's *literally* a god, right?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "His name is Francis. And that... how could you possibly come to that conclusion? Do you know nothing of the religion that you've decided to throw away?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "Nobody is 'a god'."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content:
"Yes.... I am not without fault. Certainly. Even beyond the sin inherent to all of us mortals. But I have been selected as a messenger. Even I cannot fully say why." The Pope speaks solemnly.

"Isn't it like, elections? Right? That's how people get power here?" Bernard.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "You could call it an election. God elects, Francis fulfils."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "We are all His constituents."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "There is no perfect choice. But God is unique in the lack of duress He is under. That's what allows for this."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content:
"Huh? No, that's how like, kings are 'elected'. He's not a king, he's a Pope. They're different. Right?"

"I am technically the king of the Vatican, legally speaking." The Pope clarifies the politics of the smallest nation on earth.

"What the fuck?!" Bernard almost loses focus driving. "This whole time, I've been all buddy-buddy with... ghrk."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "Bernard, are you from this reality?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: This calms him down some. "Hah. I've lost track at this point, but I'd say personally that I'm probably not."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Francis, why would you associate with someone from the reality you say is overtaking the one put in place by our God? He is representative of a state of being encroaching on our own. And he seems to have no substantial reason to be doing this that isn't likely to be corrupt in some form or another."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "Every sign points to one location."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content:
"He is... misinformed." Pope Francis shakes his head.

"I'm not a child. It's about nature vs nurture. Even if you're right that I was born on Earth, it's not where I'm from. You should trust Vito on this, if you're going to find any reason to ditch me anyway."
The car stops. The Vatican has been arrived at.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

“That… would not be entirely fair. The entities that have kidnapped and defiled you and several others have no meaningful affiliation with the UN, by all appearances. But their means trace back to initial funding and assets from a branch of it. I cannot cast an entirely unempathetic judgement on them; a man I respect was involved early on, before they could understand the depravity of their actions.” He stops on a particular segment of what he’s flipping through.
“I apologize if this brings up unpleasant memories, but… in your recent misfortune, did you ever encounter a woman named *Bonita*?”

messages.content: He slowly starts to get to his feet. "Well, maybe I do, maybe I don't. His Holiness is correct that you are in no position to make demands here, you know."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: “What, gonna arrest me?” She smirks.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: He considers the option.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: ((apparently someone tried to perform a citizen's arrest on the pope in 2010))

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: ((wish they had succeeded))

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "No, but I'm not the one who came in here with a desire to be fulfilled. I am with the current, and you are against it. As I said... no position. And the only one here with something to lose is you."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: “I don’t have a single thing to lose. Believe me.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "What you have to lose is a lack of gain. The same thing, in reality. Do you want that information or not?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: “Obviously I do.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Then, do you understand the error of your phrasing?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: “No, not really. By that logic, everyone has an endless amount to lose, because they could theoretically be gaining.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "That's the very concept of opportunity cost, I believe, yes. But there are scales of importance, points where the loss is important to life and to debate. And what I've listed is something directly relevant to a point you're making, which you were prior ignoring. Better an overestimate than underestimate, correct? For if you believe you have nothing to lose, then you must be prepared to lose everything."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content:
“You’re saying…” She quiets down into silence. Then she laughs.
“Oh my God. Holy shit, that’s *you*.” The Pope shakes his head at the use of the Lord’s name in vain to indicate he does not approve, but doesn’t interrupt.

“I mean, that’s what this is, right?” Violetta smirks, leaning against the wall.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "No, my phrasing is fine." Viotto has managed to fully stand up by this point without breaking anything.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: “Right, right. So I suffer loss, so I give up on everything else… yeah, I guess so. When you put it like that.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "And what loss is that?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: “Which one? It was a building for you. I guess what was in it was more important…”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "This topic feels as though it's going nowhere. Can you cut to the chase already?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: “Someone important to me died. It’s been a long journey since that day to be able to find the truth and accept it.” Her expression hardens. “I’ve been ready to lose everything for a very long time.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Accepting a prior loss would only make your aversion to future losses stronger, I'd think. Unless you plan on taking that long journey another hundred times over?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: She buries her face in her hand. “What even is this? This conversation here? Yeah, I don’t want to lose what I have now, but short of me getting amnesia, that won’t happen.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "You have nothing to lose, and yet... you don't wish to lose what you have?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "I suppose I can understand that."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: He goes to put his arm around her shoulders. What a troubled mindset.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content:
She flinches, but doesn’t push him away.

“Why is John Leiblich dead…?” The pope murmurs, finally saying something again.

“I don’t know. Murdered, but the killer got away. Why was John Leiblich in some insane illuminati-type shit under a fake name?”

The Pope does not have an answer to this.

Violetta addresses Viotto again. “I’m pretty sure she hates you, man. Magnolia.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: He ignores her. "Are you sure it wasn't an elaborate suicide?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content:
“Not likely. It wasn’t the type of wound common for that, and from what I could get my hands on as a mere civilian, there *is* evidence someone broke in. I don’t know if he’s the type of guy that’d…”

“No. Unthinkable.” The pope shook his head. “John Leiblich had a wife and daughter. Even if they were estranged… he’s just an uncommonly determined sort of man. I do not believe he’d give up on his goals.”

“I see. Thanks, The Pope.” Violetta.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Could it have been an accident? A struggle that took place after the break-in occurred for some other purpose? Say, theft."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "I merely think this is a hasty leap. That simply because you had knowledge of his conspiratorial lifestyle, that must mean that any event in his life must also be conspiratorial in nature."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: “It was a knife wound. Would be one hell of an accident. But yeah, I don’t know why he died, and I don’t care unless more information comes up.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Of course a burglar would carry a knife. I didn't mean that he slipped and fell, I meant that it wasn't the goal of the intrusion."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "Was the murder weapon ever located?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "And what do you *mean* you don't care? You're the one who... barged in here and attacked his Holiness with this information!"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "If you don't care, you shouldn't have ruined this!"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content:
“It was checking something else, actually. Because his real birth name shouldn’t be John Leiblich.” 

The Pope stares ambiguously.

“What am I ruining, exactly? What was going on here before I showed up, huh?”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Something with purpose! Clearly!"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "If you have nothing to add beyond empty questions with no answer, then please, just leave us be."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content:
“Heh. I don’t hate you, Viotto. Not really. It’s never really felt like my business. But you’re pretty damn hard to like.”

She gets up, walking over to the place she came in from. “Fine. Just one last question, okay? This one’s gotta have an answer.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Every question has an answer."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: “Then I suppose I wasn’t adding questions without ones.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "Just because an answer exists doesn't mean it comes pre-attached."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "Will this next one be as rhetorical?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: “If an answer was pre-attached, the question wouldn’t need to be asked, obviously. And no, this one definitely has an answer. It relies on facts and feelings that I can’t know, but you can.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "As I said, rhetorical questions are exactly the thing you're denying the existence of, despite borrowing their aesthetics..."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content:
“When I encountered loss, I became obsessive over the details, with finding who to blame or how to really understand why things ended up the way they did. For a long time. At the end of it all, past a certain point, if there was nothing… I don’t know. Maybe I could’ve accepted that. I’m lucky there wasn’t.”
She wears a very complicated expression. “Your practice burned down. It’s an event people in my family haven’t shut up about my entire life. And you… accepted it was an accident. Or your own damn fault, even. Why? I’m not interested in the views of the police. I’m interested in you.” She stares at Viotto.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "I don't understand. Are you suggesting some kind of overarching conspiracy behind the electrical failings of a quiet medical practice?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "How deep down the rabbit hole have you fallen...?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content:
“Yeah. That’s fine. It’s only ever what someone thinks that matters. Whatever. I’m not suggesting anything.”
She checks her phone. “That far south already? Dammit. This was nothing but a waste of time. Well, you two lovebirds have fun. I need to go fight a villain.” Violetta, if not stopped by Viotto, exits.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: He moves to stop her.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: She smirks. “What? Something to say?”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Could you rephrase the question? I didn't quite understand it."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: “I’m sure you’d give a straight answer if I said it differently, yeah. Here it is: Are you a masochist? Not in a sexual sense. Spiritually, in the way you might call a stereotypical monk.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "No."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: “Okay, great. That answers that.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "That doesn't seem very similar to the original question, though."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: “Maybe I’m just inefficient at communication.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "It seems likely."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "Is that all?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: “You’re the one who stopped me, man.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "You're the one who came in here on some mission, I believe."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: “It’s over. I got everything I could feasibly hope to.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "You ought to aspire to more, then."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: “I’m in the middle of that, yeah.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Then there's more you hope for, no?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: “Yes, I didn’t add ‘here’ to my earlier sentence, which clearly tripped you up.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Should we move somewhere else to discuss?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: He gives the pope a side-eye.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: ((directed at Violetta?))

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: ((yes))

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content:
She looks between you and the pope and shrugs. “I’m leaving this room. You can do as you please.”

The Pope does not react.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Viotto stands in place.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: Violetta just sort of walks. Around you?

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: He shuffles around a bit, but ultimately lets her pass.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "So... where were we?" (directed at el pope)

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: “Ah. Well…” He thinks to himself for a moment. “I don’t have anything imminent to ask of you. I could provide directions to the accommodations I’ve arranged for, if you’d like.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "That would be fantastic. To be honest, I'm quite exhausted."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: The Pope provides detailed instructions on how to get there from this exact location. They’re decent directions.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Viotto attempts to commit them to memory. We'll see how this turns out.

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: Okay.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: “Oh! Yeah, um… really got two worlds of trouble, with that, see… Well, main thing, I have this friend who works a job with animals, and he told me to cover his shift, but I don’t actually know how to do… anything.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: “Soon…? I guess not until tomorrow.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "That... is quite the predicament. It's unfortunate that you've taken so long to seek advice, but I can certainly help in some way. I have many things to attend to... is there any time you'd be available to discuss?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: “Now. Or any other time, I guess. This is like, the only obligation I have here.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "What do you need to know?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: “Well, first, I gotta feed a bunch of guys. How do I know like… which ones eat meat and which eat plants? Because I know definitely some are discerning.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Well, the general advice is to observe their front teeth. If they are pointed and sharp, they are designed for meat; whereas if they are flat, they are designed for fibrous plants."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "A bit basic, though, isn't that? Why were you entrusted this... to begin with?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "Are you sure you even need to feed these animals? It's possible your... friend would have done so in advance. There are not many animals that would do poorly on missing a singular day of food if they had been stocked up the night prior."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content:
“Oh, I see. And that’s we we have both kinds of teeth. You make a good point, I doubt he’d really give me this with no explanation if it was vital. I guess maybe it was just in case. He’s not really very good at it either, sorta had it thrust onto him. Probably doesn’t know how much, uh, leeway, he has, in when he does things.” 

Jorge puts his finger to his chin. “I’ll still head there tomorrow, but I won’t risk screwing things up trying to do too much, I guess.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "There is much more risk associated with under-feeding than over-feeding, of course. Ah, here's a solution - just give each animal a selection of both carnivorous and herbivorous food. They can discern on their own, of course. Assuming you haven't been given ultra-processed pellets, or something of the sort, ha!"

author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Ah. "Typical."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: "What's your name, then?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content: Viotto finds himself in a small, dusty, familiar cramped room with Gratia. This location was in Viotto 1, but that was such a convoluted ordeal that he may not truly appreciate this callback.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Is this part of the fallen ship we were on, then? Do you expect to navigate the rooms?"

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png

messages.content:
"I don't know where this is...?" Gratia looks around, befuddled.
There is in fact a way out of this room, to be clear, it isn't some prison.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "You should... try asking the man back there. He seemed to know, if nothing else."

author.name: v_entenmann
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\20b83a35b4910b5eb78d21e494ba8aac-2A6FD.png
